data.description: Pride of ownership! This immaculately maintained property is move-in ready. Beautiful home conveniently located in the desirable neighborhood of Cherokee Station (centrally located and near a golf course). Very popular open floor plan concept. Spacious and bright open living room and bathroom located downstairs, including entertainment kitchen; upgraded granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs you will find a grand master suite with a large master bathroom; double vanity, large stand up shower, relaxing garden tub & large walk-in closet. Two great size additional bedrooms, full bathroom and laundry room (conveniently located near the bedrooms). Lovely and manageable fenced backyard (irrigation is a bonus).
